| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2149 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 47d96bbf-a034-5bcc-90c7-b3b832a3f6bb"
